HEADWORD: non-stick
<hw>non-stick</hw></mhw> <pos>adj.</pos>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>permitting easy removal of adherent food particles; --
of surfaces, especially of cooking utensils; <as>as, a frying pan with a
<ex>nonstick</ex> surface</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
